{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "霍普（教会骑士Ver.） 第5话 尽己所能",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "扎托拉斯地区\\n山中村落",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "喝！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "终于告一段落了吗……\\n不过，魔兽实在太多了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "虽然急忙赶了过来，\\n但这副样子……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "不容乐观啊……\\n要是能找到幸存者就好了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "呜……妈、妈……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120062_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "还有呼吸……\\n可这种伤势在这么冷的环境下，\\n肯定也活不久了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120062_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "治愈之力……已经用尽了。\\n援兵应该也赶不上吧……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120062_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "我能做的……只有为她祈祷冥福了。\\n女神伊莉雅啊，\\n请指引那她无垢的灵魂……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02",
                "120062_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "神圣治愈！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "这声音……难道是！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "哈啊、哈啊、哈啊……\\n治、治愈魔法，赶、赶上了吗！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "霍普。你怎么会在这里……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120062_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "呜……啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "活过来了。\\n能让她稳定下来吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "能！\\n活下来……给我活下来啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120062_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "呼……呼……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "看来总算是度过了危险期……\\n应该已经没事了吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "真、真的吗？\\n太好了……真是太好了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "哪怕只有一个人，\\n只要我这双手能拯救……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "霍普，你为什么回来了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "你不是受不了无法拯救的现实，\\n放弃当骑士了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "因为我“不想欺骗自己”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "什么？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "因为不想再痛苦才放弃当骑士……\\n可我就算回到了故乡\\n也一直觉得很痛苦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "已经不用再看到受伤的人了，\\n可为什么还是会觉得痛苦呢。\\n我一直都在思考原因。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "然后，我终于意识到了——\\n原来，什么都不做才是最痛苦的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "正如师父所说，\\n我这双手的确过于渺小。\\n没法拯救所有人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "但是，“无法拯救”\\n和“不去拯救”是完全不同的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "那么……我还是想挣扎一番。\\n我果然还不想放弃！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "是梦中的那个人的话……\\n让我回想起了这种心情。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "“不要欺骗自己的内心。\\n勉强自己忍耐的话”……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "“反而会让自己受伤”吗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "诶？为、为什么会知道！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "那是师父的口头禅……\\n他算不上聪明，\\n但却拥有非凡的魅力。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "能成为天翼骑士的人，\\n也许拥有着某些\\n常人看不到的东西吧……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "师、师父……诶？\\n难、难道……师父的师父\\n就是上一任天翼骑士吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "这都是过去的事了。\\n那么……你就是回想起了那些\\n才改变想法回到了战地。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "然后呢？\\n看到充满绝望的战场……\\n你想怎么做？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我想成为骑士。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "这样啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "就算痛苦也好，悲伤也罢。\\n即便如此，\\n我还是不想放弃拯救他人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我不会再逃避了。\\n所以请再给我一次\\n成为骑士的机会！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "是吗……我明白了。\\n你合格了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "在黑暗中追寻光明，才是伊莉雅的骑士。\\n你的那份觉悟……我切实地感受到了。\\n现在的你，拥有了骑士应有之心。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "之前护卫考核那件事，\\n现在就算你合格吧……\\n那你就得作为教会骑士效力了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "教会骑士霍普。当务之急\\n是清扫这片区域的魔兽。\\n能做到吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "师父！\\n是，当然能！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "呀啊！嘿！\\n小菜一碟！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝伦大主教",
            "context": "喔……那个少年，回来了啊。\\n看起来很有干劲嘛。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "是的。虽说作为骑士还不够成熟，\\n但视野多少变得开阔了一些。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "骑士的训练和祭司的修行，\\n似乎都没有懈怠……\\n他说自己的目标是成为天翼骑士。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110352_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "将来……成为超越“棋子”的存在\\n也不是没有可能。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝伦大主教",
            "context": "嗯。一个小鬼虽然不能改变什么，\\n但他的剑法已经不再迷茫。\\n如果他能彻底蜕变，也不失为一乐……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "好！新招式完成啦！\\n嘿嘿……这样有没有\\n离那个人更近了一些呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我……会继续努力的。\\n请好好看着我吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "虽然我现在才刚起步，乳臭未干。\\n但总有一天……我会振翅高飞！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}